Julián Rebolledo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juli%C3%A1n_Rebolledo 0 Julián Rebolledo (born 1972), also known as Julian Dean, is an American actor and voice talent, best known for his role as the voice of the neurotic father Jake Morgendorffer on the MTV animated series Daria and as Raul Passos in the 2012 video game, Max Payne 3.
